          "locale_text": "\"But if we succeed, what next?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "deDE",
      "text": "\"Aber falls wir Erfolg haben, was dann?\"",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-06T08:36:30.9067898Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-06T08:36:30.9067899Z",
      "original_text": "\"But if we succeed, what next?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-06T08:36:30.9067905Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Aber falls wir Erfolg haben, was dann?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Mais si nous réussissons, que ferons-nous ensuite ? »",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-06T08:39:59.8805143Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-06T08:39:59.8805144Z",
      "original_text": "\"But if we succeed, what next?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-06T08:39:59.8805150Z",
          "locale_text": "« Mais si nous réussissons, que ferons-nous ensuite ? »"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«Pero, si triunfamos, ¿qué ocurrirá después?».",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-06T08:44:18.9058617Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-06T08:44:18.9058619Z",
      "original_text": "\"But if we succeed, what next?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-06T08:44:18.9058626Z",
          "locale_text": "«Pero, si triunfamos, ¿qué ocurrirá después?»."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "trTR",
      "text": "\"Diyelim ki başardık, sonra ne olacak?\"",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-06T08:45:42.2790517Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-06T08:45:42.2790519Z",
      "original_text": "\"But if we succeed, what next?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-06T08:45:42.2790524Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Diyelim ki başardık, sonra ne olacak?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“可就算我们成功了，之后又该如何？”",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-06T08:48:13.1916818Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-06T08:48:13.1916820Z",
      "original_text": "\"But if we succeed, what next?\"",
